{
  "chapter": 16,
  "chapter_summary": "第十六回 血染白衣。波娃默默离去，班察巴那告诫小方不要再见她。卜鹰白衣渗血，负伤倒地——他与无名剑客独孤痴交过手，被一剑刺伤胸膛，形容此剑为\"必杀、必胜、必死\"。卜鹰向小方坦诚相告：独孤痴痴于剑而非痴于情，痴情者必死于痴剑者之手；浪子的最大弱点是空虚孤独，一旦抓住不愿放手反而会沉得更快。卜鹰称小方为朋友，二人共饮古城烧，卜鹰吟诵藏族诗人密勒日巴名句。卜鹰揭露波娃名字意为雪、雪即水银，暗示波娃深藏不露。卫天鹏调集人马于险隘\"死颈\"设伏，卜鹰决定以逸待劳，在三十里外扎营等敌来攻。班察巴那侦察回报：七十名骑手精锐尽出，更有三顶轿子载来三位绝顶高手——波娃、一位白发如银却面容如少女的独臂独腿女子、一位能发现班察巴那藏身之处的瞎子。卜鹰白衣上鲜血不断渗出，大战将临。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "如果我是你，我也会像你这么做的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "可是如果我是你，以后我绝不会再见她。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "你受了伤？你怎么会受伤！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "只要是人，就会受伤。利剑刺入胸膛，无论谁都会受伤的。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "江湖中人都说你是从来不败的，我也知道你身经百战，从未败过一次。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "每件事都有第一次。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "是谁刺伤了你！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "你已经跟他交过手？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "当代的七大剑客，我都见过，虽然我并没有跟他们交手，但是他们的剑法我都见过。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 59
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "他们之中，有的人已老，有的人生活太奢华，有的人剑法太拘谨，昔年被江湖公认的当代七大剑客，如今都已过去，所以我没有跟他们交手，因为我知道我一定能胜过他们。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "他呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我已经跟他交过手。我敢保证，七大剑客中，绝没有一个人能接得住他这一剑的……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我从未见过那样的剑法，我连想都没有想到过。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 75
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我只能用六个字来形容这一剑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 77
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "哪六个字？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "必杀！必胜！必死！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "可是你还没有死。我看得出你绝不会死的。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你怎的看得出我不会死？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我留下你，说不定就是为了要你在这里等我死，因为我也曾留在你身边，等着你死。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "我等你。不是等你死，是等你站起来。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 103
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "有两件事，一定要告诉你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "你说。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "那个无名的剑客并不是真的没有名字，他姓独孤，叫独孤痴，不是痴于情．是痴于剑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 115
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "所以你千万不能与他交手，痴于情的人，一定会死在痴于剑的人之剑下，这一点你绝对不能不信。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 119
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "第二件事呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你是个浪子。有的浪子多金，有的浪子多情，有的浪子爱笑，有的浪子爱哭，不过所有的浪子都有一点相同。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 127
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "哪一点？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "空虚。孤独、寂寞、空虚。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "所以浪子们如果找到一个可以让自己觉得不再孤独的人，就会像一个溺水者抓到一根木头，死也不肯放手了，至于这根木头是不是能载他到岸，他并不在乎，因为他心里已经有了很安全的感觉，对浪子们来说，这已足够。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "可是你抓到的那根木头，有时非但不能载你到岸，反而会让你沉得更快，所以你应该放手时，就一定要放手。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 147
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "你为什么要对我说这些话？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "因为你是我的朋友。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "这是天山北路的古城烧。这种酒比大曲还烈得多。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你怕不怕醉？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "连死都不怕，为什么要怕醉？",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "儿须有名，酒须醉，醉后畅谈，是心言。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "还有件事我一定要告诉你。不管你信不信，我都要告诉你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 193
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "波娃的意思是雪，雪是水结成的，雪的颜色洁白如银。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "波娃才是真正的水银。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "失劫的黄金还没有找到，卫天鹏还是不会放过我，死去的儿子永远不能复生，吕三也一定不会放过你。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "现在我们'箭组'中的人已伤亡大半，他们绝不会让我们平安回到拉萨去的。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "如果我算得不错，他们此刻一定已经在那里等着我！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 219
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "你准备闯过去？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "他们就想我闯过去，我为什么要让他们称心如愿？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "除了那隘口外，还有没有别的路可走？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "没有。但是我们并不是一定非过去不可。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "不过去又如何？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "等。我们也可以等，等他们来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "他们会来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "一定会来，而且很快就会来，因为我们能等，他们不能。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "他们的人手已集中，正是士饱马腾，斗志最旺盛的时候，他们算准了这一战必胜，一击得手后，就可以开宴庆功了，所以他们身上绝不会带着太多粮食和水，因为这一战过后，我们的粮食和水就全都是他们的了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "所以他们不能等，我们不过去，他们一定会过来。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 249
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "然后呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我已吩咐过，在那隘口三十里之外扎营。他们等不到我们，斗志已衰，再奔驰三十里来找我们，气力也已弱，我们就在那里以逸待劳，等他们来送死……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "他们就算来了，也未必是来送死的。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "卫天鹏既然已决心要胜这一战，这一次必定精锐尽出，再加上独孤痴和搜魂手，我们这边能跟他们一决胜负的人有几个？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 265
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我知道不管这一战我们有多大机会，你都绝不会走的，否则你也不必为我担心了。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我受了伤。我们的人手的确不够，但是我们并不是完全没有机会。因为我们有一样东西是卫天鹏他们绝对没有的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我们有生死与共，死也不会临阵脱逃的朋友。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "不管怎么样，这次你一定要将独孤痴留给我。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "这次独孤痴恐怕不会来。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "为什么！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你一定也听过班察巴那最喜欢说的一句话。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我承认独孤痴是天下无双的剑客，可是他要让我流血，他自己也得付出代价。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "他也受了伤？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "不管怎么样，如果他来了，我一定把他留给你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "此刻已到了那里的，大约有七十匹马。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 337
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "那些人每一个都是驰术精绝的壮士，其中有一部分用的是长枪大戟，有一部分配着弓弩，还有七八个用的是外门兵刃。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 343
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "可是真正可怕的绝不是他们。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "text": "真正可怕的是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "除了七十匹马外，还有三顶轿子也到了那里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "text": "轿子里有人？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "有。一顶轿子一个人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "text": "是些什么样的人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "能够让卫天鹏派轿子去接来的，当然都是了不起的人。我只认得出其中一个。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "text": "你认得出是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "就是你认为绝不会杀人的那个女人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "除了她之外，另外一个是独臂独腿的残废，左腿上装着根木脚，右手上提着个黄布包袱，分量看来很重。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "text": "他有多大年纪？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我看不出他的年纪。他的头发每一根都白了，亮如银丝，但是一张脸却还是白里透红，看来简直是个小姑娘。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "text": "小姑娘？你说的这个人，是个女人？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "是，是个女人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "text": "另外还有一个呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "那个人好像是个瞎子，下轿时却要人搀扶，但是惟一发现我躲在附近的人就是他。我差一点就回不来了。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "text": "你累了，来喝杯酒。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 408
    }
